#: frm_telnet.cpp:686
msgid ""
"BBMan format message allow you to send special code at [auto send message "
"after connect] or [send customer message] \n"
"\n"
"All special code start with backlash \\ \n"
"\\n:[Enter]\n"
"\\^?:Ctrl+? (for example: \\^R means Ctrl+R) \n"
"\\#{UDLR}:up down left right arrow key (\\#U: up arrow) (\\#L:left arrow) \n"
"\\p3: pause for 3 secs (from 1 ~ 9)\n"
"\\\\:backlash \\\n"
"\n"
"For example when you login ptt, you can assign auto send string:\\p3username"
"\\npassword\\n\\n\\#D\\#D\\n\\n \n"
"(Pause 3 secs -> Send username -> [Enter] -> Send password -> [Enter]  login "
"-> [Enter] -> [Down] twice -> [Enter] twice to User menu)"
msgstr "BBMan 格式化訊息可以讓你在 [連線後自動送出字串] 或 [送出自定訊息] 時指定送出一些特殊碼\n\n所有特殊碼皆以斜線 \\ 為開頭\n\\n：[Enter]鍵\n\\^?：Ctrl+? ( 例如 \\^R 表示 Ctrl+R )\n\\#{UDLR}：上下左右鍵 ( \\#U：上 ) (\\#L：左)\n\\p3：暫停 3 秒 ( 數字可為 1~9 )\n\\\\：斜線 \\\n\n例如在登入 ptt 時你可以指定自動送出字串：\\p3username\\npassword\\n\\n\\#D\\#D\\n\\n \n( 暫停 3 秒 -> 輸出 username -> [Enter] -> 輸出 password -> [Enter] 登入 -> [Enter] -> 兩次 [Down] -> 兩次 [Enter] 到使用者選單 )"

