"Please enter site address\n"
"\n"
"If not connects with default port (23), please add colon and port number\n"
"For example: use ptt.twbbs.org:3456 to connect ptt.twbbs.org with port 3456"
msgstr "請輸入主機位址\n\n如果欲使用非預設 port (23) 登入，請在網址後加上 冒號: 以及 port number\n例如ptt.twbbs.org:3456 代表以 port 3456 連上 ptt.twbbs.org"

