#: frm_telnet.cpp:1094
msgid ""
"This program has built in auto reconnect function.\n"
"Some BBS (like KKCity) is hard to connect for sometime. This program will "
"retry connecting till connected. "
msgstr "此程式已內建自動重新連線機制。\n某些 BBS （例如 KKCity） 在某些時段常常會無法連上，這時此程式會自動重新連線，直到連上為止。"

#: frm_telnet.cpp:1097
msgid ""
"This program has built in prevent idle (prevent disconnect) function.\n"
"Program will send Ctrl+L every 3 minutes to make server refresh screen. "
"(Won't change your screen) Even idle for all day long you won't get "
"disconneted."
msgstr "此程式已內建防呆 (防斷線) 機制。\n程式會在閒置時每三分鐘自動丟出 Ctrl+L 讓 server 重新送一次畫面回來（而這個指令不會讓螢幕的資料有所變化），即使閒置一整天也不會被斷線。"

