#: login.cpp:150
msgid ""
"Please enter login name.\n"
"\n"
"Press Esc to log in anonymously.\n"
"\n"
" Enter 'new' to add new account.\n"
"\n"
"If you don't want this window shows every time at startup, please change it "
"in menu [Connect] -> [Login Option]."
msgstr "請輸入登入帳號\n\n直接按 Esc 代表匿名登入\n\n輸入 new 代表新增帳號\n\n若不希望每次開啟程式都出現此視窗，可到連線視窗的選單 [連線] -> [登入設定] 取消之"

